! Aperture-stop drawing: a STO on a flat air-air "dummy" surface must render as
! the traditional two-bar stop symbol in the lens layout, not be skipped as an
! undrawn dummy surface.  Regression for the Bentley5p5-style stop (surface 3).
LEN NEW
TIT 'StopDrawTest'
EPD 10.0
INS S2..5
RDY S1         60
THI S1         6
GLA S1         NSK16_SCHOTT
RDY S2         -150
THI S2         18
THI S3         18
STO S3
RDY S4         150
THI S4         6
GLA S4         NSK16_SCHOTT
RDY S5         -60
CIR S1 5
CIR S2 5
CIR S4 5
CIR S5 5
PIM
VIE
GO
